                                    "val" : {"type" : "LSString", "value" : "A long room, the edges blurred by shadow. A solitary figure sits the throne at the other end - QUEEN VLAAKITH of the githyanki, looking utterly bored.\r\nThe camera creeps towards her as she begins to stir herself at some disruption."}
