                                    "val" : {"type" : "LSString", "value" : "Psionics pulse. Two githyanki warriors, bloodied from battle, rise from the back of the kneeling crowd and loyally join her at her side as an honour guard. Lae'zel  then turns her back on the crowds, gazing outwards instead - UPWARDS."}
